\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39701,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/05\/kitab-allah-intercedes\/","url_meta":{"origin":37990,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Book of Allah intercedes for its reciters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRecite the Quran, for it is the most excellent intercessor on the Day of Resurrection. It will say: O Lord, adorn him with the noblest of ornaments! Thus, he will be adorned with the noblest of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32429,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/22\/abdullah-moderate-sunnah-bidah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37990,"position":3},"title":"Abdullah on Bid\u2019ah: Moderate Sunnah better than striving in Bid\u2019ah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahmah ibn Yazid reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cModeration in the Sunnah is better than striving in innovation.\u201d Source: al-Mustadrak 289 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647